data.description: MOTIVATED TO MOVE! Check out that PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Less than 2 miles from ALL the conveniences of town, yet OUTSIDE CITY LIMITS & TAXES, this 2 story, 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home sits on a LARGE LOT, under the shade of SPRAWLING OAKS, in a QUIET, COUNTRY NEIGHBORHOOD. Beat the Texas heat with a HVAC UPDATE in 2022 & a COVERED BACK PATIO, adjoining the INGROUND POOL, a hidden oasis behind the PRIVACY FENCED BACKYARD. Oversized, ACCESSIBLE  PRIMARY bedroom is downstairs with ensuite bathroom that includes WALKIN SHOWER, DUAL SINKS & WALKIN CLOSETS. KITCHEN IS STOCKED with AMPLE STORAGE between cabinets a plenty, double closet pantries, wet bar, sizable island & even includes the FRIDGE! Detached, 2 car, electric garage  has additional ATTIC STORAGE space as well. Look no further for your NEW HOME SWEET HOME in beautiful Athens, Texas! Check out the virtual tour on my YouTube channel @DanaeOglesby
